(ACME HVAC Manual - Model AC-3000
Chapter 1: Condenser Unit
Part Number: CM-450-BK compressor mount kit
A loud rattling noise from the outdoor unit often indicates loose
compressor mount bolts. Torque mount bolts to 12 Nm using kit CM-450-BK.) Tj 0 -20 Td
