(Chapter 2: Airflow and Cooling
Part Number: AF-16X25 air filter
Reduced cooling capacity is commonly caused by a clogged air filter.
Replace filter AF-16X25 every 90 days. Fan blade FB-300-AL must spin freely.) Tj 0 -20 Td
ET
