(Chapter 3: Troubleshooting
Rattling noise from outdoor unit: check compressor mount bolts CM-450-BK.
Not cooling properly: replace air filter AF-16X25 and check refrigerant charge.
Unit not starting: inspect capacitor CP-35-440.) Tj 0 -20 Td
